act me, in game or out, I wanna ask your opinion about something.  And I have presents for you*Smile* <p><center><b><font color="#710672" face="Black Chancery" size="-1">Sarhea Greystorm</font><fontface="arial" size="-1"> <br></b><A href="http://pub15.ezboard.com/bsarscorner"><em>Halfelven Ranger </em></font></a></p></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/umadrain.showPublicProfile?language=EN>madrain</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Kerran Lord</span><br>  Posts: 107<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(12/26/01 4:26:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=945.topic&index=12>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: We need a server event!!</span><hr size=1> *coughbumpcough*<br><br>Guildwars are few to nil that I've seen.  A few good sized guilds should get into it.  It need not be good vs evil, even.  Maybe 1st Fist of Light members insulted Starspun members and things escalated into an organized battle.  Have even sides, everyone lined up, then a neutral party yells go and everyone haves at it.<br><br>Me, I'm still looking for some Erudites to roleplay against.  I had great fun harrowing Erys of the Nexus of the Resolution guild, though I was greatly outleveled.<br><br>A couple of guilds could get together and plan a huge good vs evil event in maybe the Karanas.  Maybe the good guilds are planning a raid on somewhere the evils feel is sacred to them and are quite surprised when the evils show up to defend the site.  Temple of Cazic-Thule, maybe?  Erudites, Ogres, maybe even Iksar who have heard the call of their god to defend against the followers of Tunare and Mithaniel Marr. <p>Reoqim<br>Taruun of the 13th Claw<br>Firiona Vie<p><center><i>"Sings we a dance of wolfs,<br>Who smells fear and slays the coward.<br>Sings we a dance of ma